     vn sfx←{(i↑⍵)(⍵↓⍨i←¯1+⍵⍳'-')}cfg.version
     nvn←(3↑(-⍺)↓2⊃'.'⎕VFI vn)+⍺⌽0 0 1
     nvns←1↓∊'.',¨⍕¨nvn
